"title": "1441: revelation, necessity of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1441",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Finiteness and sin make it impossible to gain adequate knowledge of God through human effort alone. God in mercy makes himself known through the incarnation of the Son and the illumination of human minds to understand him.</p>\n<h2>The impossibility of fully knowing God without revelation</h2>\n<h3>God is beyond unaided human knowing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:18\">JHN 1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:20\">EXO 33:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:8-Isa55:9\">ISA 55:8–55:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:46\">JHN 6:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:12\">1JN 4:12</a></p>\n<h3>The human mind is limited</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:7\">JOB 11:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:4\">JOB 9:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:10\">JOB 9:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job23:3-Job23:9\">JOB 23:3–23:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job26:14\">JOB 26:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:26\">JOB 36:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:5\">JOB 37:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:23\">JOB 37:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:6\">PSA 139:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:3\">PSA 145:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:11\">ECC 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:13-Isa40:14\">ISA 40:13–40:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:28\">ISA 40:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:33\">ROM 11:33</a></p>\n<h3>The human mind cannot discern God of its own accord</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:5\">JHN 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18-Rom1:32\">ROM 1:18–1:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:21\">1CO 1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:14\">1CO 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:14\">2CO 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:17-Eph4:18\">EPH 4:17–4:18</a></p>\n<h2>God is known fully only through Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:1-Heb1:2\">HEB 1:1–1:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14-John1:18\">JHN 1:14–1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:3\">JHN 17:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15-Col1:20\">COL 1:15–1:20</a></p>",
